                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110918-85-off453 t18110918-85-cd454"></join>, a silver milk pot, value 2 l. a silver table spoon, value 9 s. two shawls value 6 s. and a dollar, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18110918-85-victim631" type="victimName">
                        Edward 
